## Strategic Purpose

Explain why this epic exists.

The purpose should represent this epic’s distinct portion of the original split opportunity.

Do not introduce unrelated goals.

## Desired Capability

State the capability this epic is intended to deliver or advance.

Use projection vocabulary.

Explain why this capability belongs in this epic and not a sibling epic.

## Split Rationale

Explain why this capability was separated from the original initiative.

Include:

- capability boundary
- dependency reason
- repository boundary or abstraction
- risk isolation
- strategic coherence

Do not retell the full split proposal.

## Repository Grounding

Summarize how current repository reality shapes this epic.

Include only repository findings that materially affect this epic’s scope, dependencies, constraints, or milestones.

Do not create a repository inventory.

Use concise bullets.

